---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section
    class="mt-12 py-16 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-zinc-950/50 px-8 lg:px-20"
>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
        <div class="text-center space-y-4">
            <h2
                class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 dark:text-white"
            >
                ¿Por qué usar nuestros widgets?
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-lg text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
            >
                Mejora el tiempo de permanencia y la utilidad de tu sitio web sin escribir una sola
                línea de código complejo.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:speedometer" class="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Carga Ultrarrápida</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Aislados mediante iFrame para asegurar que el rendimiento de tu web principal
                    nunca se vea afectado.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:brush-variant" class="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Diseño Adaptable</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Nuestros widgets detectan el espacio disponible y se ajustan automáticamente a
                    móviles, tablets y escritorio.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
                <div
                    class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:google" class="w-6 h-6" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Impulso SEO</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Las herramientas interactivas aumentan la interacción del usuario, un factor
                    clave para el posicionamiento en Google.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <article class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none pt-10 px-4 sm:px-0">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 text-center">
                Listos para usar en tus plataformas favoritas
            </h4>

            <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:wordpress" class="w-8 h-8 text-[#21759b] mb-2" />
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >WordPress</span
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                >
                    <Icon
                        name="mdi:notebook-outline"
                        class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2"
                    />
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Notion</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:web" class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-500 mb-2" />
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Tu Web</span>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:square" class="w-8 h-8 text-black dark:text-white mb-2" />
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >Squarespace</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
